business he is the former chairman of the board of visitors of the fuqua school of business at duke university a member of the financial services roundtable and financial services forum a member of the board of private export funding corporation and vice chairman of big brothersbig sisters of new york philanthropyedit in  hassell and his wife anitaagnes donated  million to duke university personaledit hassell is married to anitaagnes they have two children see alsoedit bank of new york referencesedit  weidner david december   correct bonymellon merger change in ceo broke the logjam marketwatch retrieved  april    company news new president an insider is named at bank of new york the new york times  september  p  retrieved  april    httpwwwbnymelloncomaboutmanagementhassellhtml  the bank of new york president gerald hassell named chair of fuqua board of visitors  dukes fuqua school of business wwwfuquadukeedu retrieved    press release wwwsecgov retrieved    httpwwwfuquadukeedualumnialumninewsnewsletter  httpwwwfuquadukeedualumnialumninewsnewsletter retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlegeraldhasselloldid categories  birthsliving peoplebank of new yorkduke university alumnistern school of business alumnihidden categories blp articles lacking sources from april all blp articles lacking sourcesarticles with hcards navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages فارسی edit links this page was last edited on  march  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license a