 of visitors of columbia university medical center and the boards of the new york philharmonic the economic club of new york and the national september  memorial  museum he is also a member of the financial services forum and is vice chairman of big brothers big sisters of new york cityexperiencechairmanbny mellonjuly  – present  monthgreater new york city areachairman and ceobny mellonseptember  – present  years  monthspresidentbny mellonjuly  – september   years  monthspresidentthe bank of new york – july   yearseducationduke universitybachelors degree economicsbachelors degree economicsnew york university  leonard n stern school of businessmaster of business administration mbamaster of business administration mbaview gerald’s full profile tosee who you know in commonget introducedcontact gerald directlyview gerald’s full profilenot the gerald you’re looking for view moreview this profile in another languageenglishgermanpeople also viewedjamie dimonchairman and ceo of jpmorgan chase  cobrian t sheavice chairman and chief executive officer investment services at bny melloneric d kambackceoevp corporate trust at bny mellonlarry finkchairman and ceo at blackrockjoie townsendglobal head of talent  development at bny mellonjames gormanchairman and ceo at morgan stanleyray daliochairman  chief investment officer at bridgewater associates lpsuresh kumarcio bny mellonmonique herenachro and sevp human resources at bny mellonerik beckmanaging director at bny mellonpublic profile badgeinclude this linkedin profile on other websitesview profile badgesfind a different gerald hassellfirst namelast nameexample gerald hasselldr gerald hassellpresident at a legacy of powerunited statesgerry hassellvp  treasury management consultant at banner bankunited statesjerry hassellowner and chief videographer at hvproductionsunited statesjerry hassellunited statesmore professionals named gerald hasselljobs similar to gerald’sbny mellon jobschairman jobslinkedin member directoryabcdefghijklm